In thoroughfares nigh the docks, any considerable seaport will
frequently offer to view the queerest (1546,8)nondescripts from foreign
parts. Even in Broadway and Chestnut(197,8), Mediterranean mariners
will sometimes jostle the affrighted ladies. Regent Street is not
