First: The uncertain, unsettled condi(885,10)is science of Cetology
is(1930,8)very vestibule attested by the fact, that in some quarters it
still remains a moot point whether a whale be a fish. In his System of
Nature, A.D. 1776, Linnæus declares, “I hereby separate the(1569,8)from
the fish.” But of(1349,8)knowledge, I know that down to the year 1850,
