were still found dividing the possess(1312,11)same sea(586,10)
L(827,8).

The grounds upon which(298,9)would fain have banished(294,21)waters, he states as follows: “On account of their warm bilocular
heart, their lungs(13,8)movable eyelid(23,9)hollow ears, penem
intrantem feminam mammis lactantem,” and finally, “ex lege naturæ jure
meritoque.” I submitted all this to my friends Simeon Macey and Charley
