they united(869,8)opinion that the reasons set forth were altogether
insufficient.(162,8) profanely hinted they were humbug.

Be it known that, waiving all argument, I take the good old fashioned
ground(178,10)whale is a fish, and call upon holy Jonah to back me.
This fundamental thing settled, the nex(1076,8)is, in what internal
respect does(139,11)differ from other fish. Above(1088,10)has given
you those items. But in brief, they are these: lungs and warm blood;
whereas, all(119,11) are lungless and cold blooded.

Next: how shall we defin(1220,11), by his obvious externals, so as
conspicuously to label him for all time to come? To be short, then, a
(458,9)_a spouting fish with a horizontal tail_. There you have him.
However contracted, that definition is the result of expanded
meditation. A walrus spouts much like(1596,8), but the(41,8)is not a
fish, because he is amphibious. But the last term(1387,8)(165,13)
still more cogent, as coupled(2007,9) first. Almost any one must have
