barrels will thy(37,10) yie(1475,8)even if thou gettest it(205,14)? it will not fetch thee much in our Nantucket market.”

“(21,16)! Hoot! But come closer(1572,12)thou requirest a
little lower layer. If money’s to be the(578,8)r, man, and the
accountants have comp(860,8)ir great counting-house the globe, by
