“What was it, Sir?” said Flask.

“The great live squid, which, they say, few whale-ships ever beheld,
and return(1979,9)ir ports to tell of it.”

But Ahab said nothing; turning his boat, he sailed back(2015,8)vessel;
the rest as silently following.

Whatever superstitions the sperm whalemen in general have(1731,8)ed
