CHAPTER 60. The Line.

With re(1103,8)to the whaling scene shortly to be(529,9)d, as well as
for the better under(1463,8) of all similar scenes elsewhere presented,
I have here to spe(204,10)magical, sometimes horrible whale-line.

The line originally used(1722,8)fishery wa(1186,9)best hemp, slightly
vapor(967,9)ar, not impregnat(993,8)it, as(1814,8)case of(1131,8)y
