admonitory stage of life, forswears, disbands(1198,10), and grown to
an exemplary, sulky old soul, goes about all alone(1794,10) meridians
and parallels saying his prayers, and warning each(1170,8)eviathan from
his amorous errors.

Now, a(196,11) of(1131,8)is called by(1128,15)a school, so is
