*B(96,11)! (14,14)This is the invariable cry(1261,10)mates
to(1494,11). It enjoins him to be careful, and cut his work into as
thin slices as possible, inasmuch as by so do(609,8)business of
boiling out the oil is much accelerated, and its quantity considerably
