now and then with(593,11)grizzled wittiness; such as might have
served to pass the time during the midnight watch (1696,8)earded
forecastle of Noah’s ark. Was it that this old(1680,11)had been a
life-long wanderer, whose much rolling, to and fro, not only had
gathered no moss; but what is more, had rubbed off whatever small
outward clinging(293,12) originally pertained to him? He was a
stript abstract; an unfractioned integral; uncompromised as a new-born
babe; living(1449,9)premeditated reference to(1229,8)rld or the next.
You might almost say,(397,11)strange(139,14)(1328,11)
involved a sort of un(1288,12); for in his numerous trades, he did
not(1381,9)work so much by reason or by instinct, or simply because he
(558,9)tutored to it, or by any intermixture of all these, even or
uneven; but merely by a kind of deaf and dumb, spontaneous literal
process.(503,9) pure manipulator; his brain(2010,8)had ever had one,
must have early oozed along(1474,9) muscles of his finger(123,9)
like one of those unreasoning but still highly useful, _multum in
parvo_, Sheffield contrivances, assum(1031,8)exterior—though a little
swelled—of a common pocket knife; but containing(956,11)blades of
various sizes, but also screw-drivers, cork-screws, tweezers, awls,
pens, rulers, nail-filers, countersinkers. So, if his superiors wanted
to use the(1198,11)for a(142,13),(610,8)y had to do was to open
that part of him,(1452,8) screw was fast: or if for(211,11)take him
up by the legs(69,9)re they were.

Yet, as previously hinted, this omnitooled, open-and-shut(1426,10),
was, after all, no mere machine of an automaton. If he did not have a
common soul(1882,9)he had a subtle something that somehow anomalously
did its duty. What that was, whether essence of quicksilver, or a few
drops of hartshorn, there is no telling. But(25,8)t was;(361,11)it
had abided for now some sixty years or more. And this it was, this same
unaccountable, cunning life-principle in him;(69,16)at kept
him a gre(609,11)(1978,9)soliloquizing; but only like an
(1061,12)wheel, which also hummingly(72,11)es; or rather, his
body was a sentry-box a(248,8)(60,11)r on guard there, and talking
all(186,10)to keep himself awake.


