these seemed the strange calm(780,8)preluding some riotous and
desperate scene.

At last, when the ship drew near to the outskirts, as it were,(644,8)Equatorial fishing-grou(1553,8)in the deep darkness that goes before
the dawn, was sailing by a cluster of rocky islets; the watch—then
