by the peaceable gush of that mystic fountain in his head, did the
White Whale now reveal his vicinity; but(1642,8)far more wondrous
phenomenon of breaching. Rising with his utmost velocity(1239,9)
furthest depths, the Sperm Whale thus booms his entire bulk into the
pure element of air(1953,8)ling up a m(268,8)of dazzling foam, shows
his place(502,8)distance of seven miles and more. In those moments,
the torn, enraged waves he shakes off, seem his mane; in some cases,
this(334,10) is his act of defiance.

